The background is blurred, predominantly red, and the surface on which the glass and saucer rest is gray.

The frame shows a close-up of a traditional Turkish tea glass placed on a matching saucer on a gray surface. The tea glass is clear and empty. To the right, a white teapot with red and blue floral designs is pouring tea into the glass. The background is a deep red color.

The background is blurred, with a reddish tone, emphasizing the focus on the tea being poured. The surface on which the glass cup and saucer rest appears to be a gray textured countertop.
